WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
I'm reading an old English story called Goldilocks and the Three Bears.

00:07.000 --> 00:09.000
Do you know it, Tony?

00:09.000 --> 00:12.760
Yes, it's very famous.

00:12.760 --> 00:19.280
Once upon a time there was a little girl with hair the colour of gold.

00:19.280 --> 00:22.240
Her name was Goldilocks.

00:22.240 --> 00:25.880
She lived near the forest.

00:25.880 --> 00:30.520
One day she decided to go for a walk.

00:30.520 --> 00:34.000
She walked into the forest with her basket.

